aboutPage.content: I am a Developer and Analyst based in Chennai, India. I'm an Artificial Intellligence and Data Science Undergraduate with expertise in Web Development and Data Analytics. I'm passionate about building and deploying AI models and creating web applications. I'm also a competitive programmer and have a good understanding of algorithms and data structures. I'm constantly pushing myself to learn new technologies and improve my skills.
